thread.title: BRIEF-Shanghai Challenge Textile sees FY 2017 net profit up 26.5 pct to 195.2 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shanghai Challenge Textile sees FY 2017 net profit up 26.5 pct to 195.2 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - shanghai challenge textile co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Shanghai Challenge Textile Co Ltd
* Says it sees net profit for FY 2017 to increase by 26.5 percent to 195.2 percent, or to be 15 million yuan to 35 million yuan
* Says the net profit of FY 2016 was 11.9 million yuan
* Comments that inclusion of new companies as main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/imQexw
